                            When did recreational cannabis become legal in Canada?
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1538408872220-when-did-recreational-cannabis-become-legal-in-canada-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1538408872220-when-did-recreational-cannabis-become-legal-in-canada-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1538408872220 stackparsys">










				
