<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="e6dbaf3f-623f-4cae-9555-adeef694de2b" >

    <p>The cultivation, sale, possession and use of recreational cannabis became legal in Canada as of<strong>&nbsp;October 17, 2018.</strong></p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#e6dbaf3f-623f-4cae-9555-adeef694de2b");});</script></div>

